oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Nathan Chapman - 2017-07-22
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by Nathan Chapman from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on July 22, 2017. Includes guest performances from Mickey Guyton, Liz Rose and Stephanie Chapman. Includes questions from the audience.
